{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/study-blog/css-box-model/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<p>모든 HTML 요소를 감싸는 상자</p>\n<h1>Box의 구성</h1>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6ee8df1750162c354d9b3a2e0c5c7ad5/c6e0f/box-model.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/6ee8df1750162c354d9b3a2e0c5c7ad5/a59e9/box-model.webp 192w,\n/static/6ee8df1750162c354d9b3a2e0c5c7ad5/0ca9f/box-model.webp 384w,\n/static/6ee8df1750162c354d9b3a2e0c5c7ad5/dc9b9/box-model.webp 768w,\n/static/6ee8df1750162c354d9b3a2e0c5c7ad5/e2c2f/box-model.webp 1152w,\n/static/6ee8df1750162c354d9b3a2e0c5c7ad5/c9fa7/box-model.webp 1416w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/6ee8df1750162c354d9b3a2e0c5c7ad5/3b721/box-model.png 192w,\n/static/6ee8df1750162c354d9b3a2e0c5c7ad5/66595/box-model.png 384w,\n/static/6ee8df1750162c354d9b3a2e0c5c7ad5/fe486/box-model.png 768w,\n/static/6ee8df1750162c354d9b3a2e0c5c7ad5/d2d74/box-model.png 1152w,\n/static/6ee8df1750162c354d9b3a2e0c5c7ad5/c6e0f/box-model.png 1416w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/6ee8df1750162c354d9b3a2e0c5c7ad5/fe486/box-model.png\"\n            alt=\"box\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">구성 요소</th>\n<th></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">Content</td>\n<td>콘텐츠가 표시되는 영역<br />글, 이미지, 비디오 등의 실제 내용<br />배경색, 배경 이미지 포함<br /> <code class=\"language-text\">width</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">height</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">Padding</td>\n<td>콘텐츠 주변의 여백 영역<br />콘텐츠 영역을 요소의 안쪽 여백까지 포함하는 크기로 확장<br /><code class=\"language-text\">padding</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">Border</td>\n<td>콘텐츠와 패딩을 둘러싼 테두리 영역<br /><code class=\"language-text\">border</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">Margin</td>\n<td>콘텐츠, 패딩, 테두리를 둘러싼 가장 바깥 쪽 영역<br />다른 요소 사이의 공백 역할<br /><code class=\"language-text\">margin</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h1>유형</h1>\n<h2>표준 박스 모델(Standard box model)</h2>\n<p>브라우저의 기본 박스 모델</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>속성 (기본값, 생략 가능)</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">box-sizing: content-box</code></p>\n<p>width, height 속성이 content 영역만 포함</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>크기 계산</p>\n<ul>\n<li>너비 = width + padding + border</li>\n<li>높이 = height + padding + border</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.content-box</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> goldenrod<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 350px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 150px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 25px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 25px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5px solid black<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 424px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e20db385812038b96dbabc60702bc4f8/4910e/content-box.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64.58333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/e20db385812038b96dbabc60702bc4f8/a59e9/content-box.webp 192w,\n/static/e20db385812038b96dbabc60702bc4f8/0ca9f/content-box.webp 384w,\n/static/e20db385812038b96dbabc60702bc4f8/a784c/content-box.webp 424w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 424px) 100vw, 424px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/e20db385812038b96dbabc60702bc4f8/3b721/content-box.png 192w,\n/static/e20db385812038b96dbabc60702bc4f8/66595/content-box.png 384w,\n/static/e20db385812038b96dbabc60702bc4f8/4910e/content-box.png 424w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 424px) 100vw, 424px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/e20db385812038b96dbabc60702bc4f8/4910e/content-box.png\"\n            alt=\"content\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>총 너비 = 5 + 25 + 350 + 25 + 5 = 410px</p>\n<p>총 높이 = 5 + 25 + 150 + 25 + 5 = 210px</p>\n<h2>대체 박스 모델(Alternative box model)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>속성</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">box-sizing: border-box</code></p>\n<p>width, height 속성이 content, padding, border 영역을 포함 (margin 포함 X)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>크기 계산</p>\n<ul>\n<li>너비 = width</li>\n<li>높이 = height</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.border-box</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> goldenrod<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 350px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 150px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 25px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 25px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5px solid black<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token property\">box-sizing</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> border-box<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 426px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0085bae282185141e6812ea2c3b77fb5/28e10/border-box.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/0085bae282185141e6812ea2c3b77fb5/a59e9/border-box.webp 192w,\n/static/0085bae282185141e6812ea2c3b77fb5/0ca9f/border-box.webp 384w,\n/static/0085bae282185141e6812ea2c3b77fb5/039b3/border-box.webp 426w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 426px) 100vw, 426px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/0085bae282185141e6812ea2c3b77fb5/3b721/border-box.png 192w,\n/static/0085bae282185141e6812ea2c3b77fb5/66595/border-box.png 384w,\n/static/0085bae282185141e6812ea2c3b77fb5/28e10/border-box.png 426w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 426px) 100vw, 426px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/0085bae282185141e6812ea2c3b77fb5/28e10/border-box.png\"\n            alt=\"border\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>총 너비 = 5 + 25 + 290 + 25 + 5 = 350px</p>\n<p>총 높이 = 5 + 25 + 90 + 25 + 5 = 150px</p>\n<h1>참고</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Learn/CSS/Building_blocks/The_box_model\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">The box model - Learn web development | MDN</a>